.. _intro_R:


*****************************
Introduction to R and Rstudio
*****************************

.. _install_Rstudio:

Install Rstudio
---------------
Hopefully, you have downloaded R and Rstudio already. If you do have chance
for it. Download R from `R <https://cran.rstudio.com/`_ and 
Rstudio from  `Rstudio <https://www.rstudio.com/products/rstudio/download3/>`_.
Please check your Operation System before downloading.



   
